1. Privremeno ću ti dati ovu knjigu dok ne kupiš svoju. (*Privremeno* - adverb at the beginning of the sentence) (I will *temporarily* give you this book until you buy your own.)
2. Uradili smo samo privremene popravke na krovu. (privremene - adjective in plural form) (We have done only *temporary* repairs to the roof.)
3. Moraćemo privremeno da se preselimo dok se ne završi obnova kuće. (*privremeno* - adverb in the middle of the sentence) (We will have to *temporarily* move until the house renovation is completed.)
4. Privremeni posao mi je omogućio da zaradim novac za putovanje. (Privremeni - adjective in singular form) (The *temporary* job allowed me to earn money for the trip.)
5. U toku privremene suspenzije nećete moći da koristite svoj nalog. (*privremene* - adjective in feminine gender) (During the *temporary* suspension, you will not be able to use your account.)